CatDescriptText: Related image published in advertisement in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 6, 1954, pg. 11, with text: "Another order of that fine Crayton's sausage for Brown's Superette.  You'll smile, too, when you taste the real down-to-earth goodness of Crayton's sausage, call Fentco Distributors, 721 Larimer Ave., Phone EM 1-4583."
TitMainTitle: Delivery man handing Crayton's sausages to shop keeper at meat counter in store with sign advertising Hog Malls and Heinz products, possibly in Brown's Superette
